ch  )."],"variants":[{"name":"Ferg","meanings":["From the vocabulary word denoting the plant (Old English <i>fearn</i>). Modern use of this word as a given name dates from the 19th century, when it is also recorded occasionally as a boy's name in the United States. In some instances the given name may be a transferred use of the surname derived in the medieval period from the vocabulary word."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Margred ferch Dafydd was born about 1225, in Pembrey, Carmarthenshire, Wales as the daughter of Dafydd ap Adam. She had at least 1 son with Ieuan ap Dafydd."},"et":{"about 1225–":"umbes 1225–Surnud","1225–Female":"1225–Surnud","–Male":"Surnud","1240–Male":"1240–Surnud","1225":"1225","about 1225":"umbes 1225","1240":"1240","Glyncorrwg, , Glamorgan, Wales, United Kingdom":"Glyncorrwg, Glamorgan, Wales, United Kingdom","of Trimsaran,Pen-bre,Carmarthenshire,Wales":"Pembrey, Carmarthenshire, Wales"},"fi":{"about 1225–":"noin 1225–Kuollut","1225–Female":"1225–Kuollut","–Male":"Kuollut","1240–Male":"1240–Kuollut","1225":"1225","about 1225":"noin 1225","1240":"1240","Glyncorrwg, , Glamorgan, Wales, United Kingdom":"Glyncorrwg, Glamorgan, Wales, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","of Trimsaran,Pen-bre,Carmarthenshire,Wales":"Pembrey, Carmarthenshire, Wales"},"fr":{"about 1225–":"environ 1225–Décédée","1225–Female":"1225–Décédée","–Male":"Décédé","1240–Male":"1240–Décédé","1225":"1225","about 1225":"environ 1225","1240":"1240","Glyncorrwg, , Glamorgan, Wales, United Kingdom":"Glyncorrwg, Glamorgan, Pays de Galles, Royaume-Uni","of Trimsaran,Pen-bre,Carmarthenshire,Wales":"Pembrey, Carmarthenshire, Galles","lifeSummary":"Margred ferch Dafydd est née environ 1225, à Pembrey, Carmarthenshire, Galles, fille de Dafydd ap Adam. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec Ieuan ap Dafydd."},"de":{"about 1225–":"um 1225–Verstorben","1225–Female":"1225–Verstorben","–Male":"Verstorben","1240–Male":"1240–Verstorben","1225":"1225","about 1225":"um 1225","1240":"1240","Glyncorrwg, , Glamorgan, Wales, 